###[CRC] Incomplete edit
If you're going to edit a post, fix all the issues not just some.

###[CRC] Bumping old posts
Do not make minor edits to old posts. It bumps them to the front page.

###[CRC] `BackTicks`
Do not edit just to add backticks. Edit posts that need substantial improvements.

###[CRC] Closed questions
Do not edit closed question, unless it brings the question on topic.

###[CRC] Off Topic questions
Do not edit off topic question, unless it brings the question on topic.

###[CRC] Minor grammar
Do not edit to make minor grammar changes. Edit posts that need substantial improvements.

###[CRC] Bulk tag edits
Do not make bulk tag edits https://meta.stackoverflow.com/questions/307928/needless-bulk-tag-edits

###[CRC] Attempt to Reply
Do not edit answers to include your own information. Post another answer instead addressing any issues.
